Consider a class 'Calculator' with both static and instance methods for addition:

```java
public class Calculator {
    // Static method
    public static int addStatic(int a, int b) {
        return a + b;
    }

    // Instance method
    public int addInstance(int a, int b) {
        return this.addStatic(a, b); // Calling static method from instance method
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int resultStatic = Calculator.addStatic(5, 3); // Calling static method
        Calculator calc = new Calculator();
